SIMPLE: unbolt
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unbolt
<hw>Un*bolt"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>bolt</ets>.]</ety> <def>To remove a bolt from; to
unfasten; to unbar; to open.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧He shall <xex>unbolt</xex> the
gates.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbolt</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unbolt
<hw>Un*bolt"</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To explain or unfold a matter;
to make a revelation.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧I will
<xex>unbolt</xex> to you.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unbone</ent>⟦br⟧
